dcterms:description: A dataset containing nearly 300,000 simulated responses generated by classical Monte Carlo methods, each with a dimension of 44x44 and includes nine properties for each particle: momentum and velocity in three planes, as well as mass, charge, and energy.
dcterms:title: Responses generated by classical Monte Carlo methods
